Tarius Johnson upon his induction into the Jackson-Madison County Sports Hall of Fame and
extend to him our best wishes for much continued success and happiness.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, that an appropriate copy of this resolution be prepared
for presentation with this final clause omitted from such copy.
